PRIVACY POLICY FOR 'TO ARMS!!' ON GOOGLE PLAY
Effective date: August 02, 2022

Latahunden provides the mobile game called “To Arms!!” (hereafter the “Game”) via Google Play (collectively referred to as the “Service”). 
This Privacy Policy is specific to the Game.

This page informs you of the privacy policy regarding the collection, use and disclosure of personal data when you use the Service and the Game. 
By using the Service, you agree to this policy.

USE OF DATA
Other than data collected to show leaderboards and achievements via Google Play Services, no data is collected or stored by me.
Leaderboards and achievements via Google Play Services is not mandatory and can be turned off under "score" menu.

Transfer Of Data
Data is transmitted to Google Play Services for the purposes of showing global leaderboards and achievements.

CHANGES TO THIS PRIVACY POLICY
If the Privacy Policy is every changed I will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page.

CONTACT ME
If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact me:

By email: latahunden@gmail.com
By visiting my reddit site: https://www.reddit.com/r/toarms/
